        Selling in Rochedale 2026
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(25,24,23,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Rochedale's modern family estates, the Rochedale State School catchment, and the older acreage pockets in the east attract a committed family buyer from across south Brisbane and interstate. Here is what sellers need to know in 2026.
      </p>
    </div>
